quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  23,51,"(This was a brief resume of some of Our Messengers. We had said to them), \"O Messengers! Partake of the decent things of life and work for the betterment of humanity. Verily, I am Aware of what you do"
  23,52,"And verily, this community of yours is one community and I am your Sustainer. So, walk aright remaining conscious of Me.\" (Since all Messengers were one Brotherhood unanimous in purpose, all mankind must consider one another as brothers and sisters)"
  23,53,"But they (who claim to follow you O Messengers) have torn their unity wide asunder, piece by piece into disputing factions, each faction rejoicing in its beliefs"
  23,54,"But leave them alone, lost in their ignorance until a time. (And the Truth will ultimately prevail (22:17)"
  23,55,"Do they think that, since We continue to provide them with wealth and children"
  23,56,"We are being swift to them with good things? Nay, but they perceive not"
  23,57,"(It is people who must hasten to do good and become worthy of good things.) Verily, those who are reverently conscious of their Lord"
  23,58,And those who have conviction in the Messages of their Lord
  23,59,And those who do not associate anyone with Him
  23,60,"And those who give (in the Cause of Allah of their wealth and person) whatever they can, and are still afraid (that they have not done enough and) because they have to return to their Lord"
  23,61,"It is they who race with one another to improve the quality of life for humanity, and it is they who are worthy of winning good things"
  23,62,"We do not hold responsible any person beyond his or her capacity. Our Commands are meant to expand your human potential. (2:286), (6:153), (7:42). And with Us is the Database that speaks the Truth (about what you can and cannot do). And none shall de wronged"
  23,63,"Nay, but their hearts are in ignorance of this Qur'an, and they are too busy doing other things and will keep doing so"
  23,64,"When We grasp their rich elite with retribution, they will moan and groan"
  23,65,"Groan not in supplication this day! You will surely, not be helped by Us"
  23,66,"My Messages were conveyed to you, but you used to turn back on your heels"
  23,67,"In arrogance, talking nonsense about these Verses like people telling fables far into the night"
  23,68,"Have they not pondered the Word? Is the Revelation something that never came to their remote forefathers, ( Noah, Abraham, Ishmael, and others)"
  23,69,"Or do they not recognize their Messenger, that they deny him"
  23,70,"Or do they say, \"There is madness in him?\" Nay, he brings them the Truth, and most of them are haters of the Truth. (They want him to make compromises (10:15), (11:113), (1)"
  23,71,"And if the Truth had followed their whims (2:120), verily the heavens and the earth and all beings therein would have fallen into ruin. Nay, We have given them their Reminder, but they turn away from their Reminder that can give them eminence. (7:176), (21:1)"
  23,72,"(O Messenger) Do you ask them for any tribute? (They must know that) your Sustainer's tribute is best, for, He is the Best of providers"
  23,73,"And, verily, you call them onto a Straight Path"
  23,74,"But, behold, those who disbelieve in the life to come are bound to deviate from that Way"
  23,75,"Even if We had mercy on them and relieved them of their suffering, they would obstinately persist in their transgression wandering to and fro"
  23,76,"And, indeed, We tested them through suffering, but they did not humble themselves before their Lord, nor implored Him"
  23,77,"Until when We open for them the gate of severe retribution, behold, they will be then completely demoralized"